{"lemma":"ز","slug":"ز","root":"NTWS","root_slug":"NTWS","root_link":"/words/roots/NTWS","pos":"N","pos_camel":"abbrev","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["character","symbol"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n17317"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"character","gloss":"The eleventh letter of the Arabic alphabet, written in the Arabic script; preceded by ر (r) and followed by س (s).","tags":["letter"]},{"pos":"symbol","gloss":"The seventh numeral symbol of the Arabic alphabet (traditional abjad order, used for list numbering), written in the Arabic script; preceded by و (w) and followed by ح (ḥ)."}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the Nabataean letter 𐢉 (l, “zayin”), derived from the Phoenician letter 𐤆 (l, “zayin”), from an uncertain Egyptian hieroglyph (𓈔?,𓏭?). See also Classical Syriac ܙ (l, “zayin”), Hebrew ז (l, “zayin”), Ancient Greek ζ (z), Latin Z."},"ipa":["/zaːj/","/zajn/","/zaːʔ/","/z/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n17317","headword_ar":"ز","root":"z","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The eleventh letter of the alphabet;"},{"kind":"text","text":"commonly called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaAYN","text_ar":"زَاىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and sometimes"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaA='N","text_ar":"زَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zFA","text_ar":"زًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaA","text_ar":"زَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaAYN","text_ar":"زَاىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zwY","text_ar":"زوى"},{"kind":"text","text":",)] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaY~N","text_ar":"زَىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaYo","text_ar":"زَىْ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (MF.) It is one of the letters termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majohuwrap","text_ar":"مَجْهُورَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or vocal, i. e. pronounced with the voice, and not with the breath only]; and of the letters termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asilay~ap","text_ar":"اَسِلَيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", because proceeding from the tip of the tongue. (TA.) Az says that it is not conjoined with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"S","text_ar":"ص"},{"kind":"text","text":"in any Arabic word. (TA.) It is substituted for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":"and for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"S","text_ar":"ص"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yazodilu","text_ar":"يَزْدِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yasodilu","text_ar":"يَسْدِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yazoduqu","text_ar":"يَزْدُقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaSoduqu","text_ar":"يَصْدُقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and in the Tes-heel it is said that it is sometimes interchanged [with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":"] after"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"j","text_ar":"ج"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jusotu xilaAla Ald~iyaAri","text_ar":"جُسْتُ خِلَالَ الدِّيَارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juzotu","text_ar":"جُزْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and after"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasaba","text_ar":"رَسَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"razaba","text_ar":"رَزَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": which interchange, accord. to MF, is said to be of the dial. of Kelb; or, as Et-Toosee says, of the dial. of 'Odhrah and Kaab and Benul-' Ambar. (TA.)       -A2-  [As a numeral,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"z","text_ar":"ز"},{"kind":"text","text":"denotes"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Seven."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}